.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, photographer, police-officer
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, magic-tricks, baking, video-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, soccer, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, tram, trike
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the electrician is the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person driving the tram is the photographer##1
4. the bartender is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person driving the car##2
5. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is the person driving the trike##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Job           | electrician | bartender | police-officer | photographer |
| Hobby   | photography  | baking | magic-tricks         | video-games      |
| Sport         | soccer      | rowing    | tennis         | ice-hockey   |
| Transport     | car         | roller    | trike          | tram         |

